title: Thin Lizzy - Live and Dangerous 1978 / Deluxe Edition
description:
Live and Dangerous is included in the book 1001 Albums You Must Hear Before You Die. 

In February 2010 Live and Dangerous was ranked number one in PlanetRock.com's The Greatest Live Album Top 40.
 
In 2011, the British music magazine NME ranked Live and Dangerous at No. 1 in its 50 Greatest Live Albums of All Time.
